i’m proposing to invest 150k (worth of DAI or ETH as the community prefers) to be used for marketing and community building. In exchange for the investment to receive 2% of tokens at genesis. Seed round was at a valuation of $2.5m , this would increase pre-launch valuation to $7.5m which reflects the work put into the technology since previous fundraising. The funds will be sent to the DAO once it is tested and deemed safe to do so on main-net, in the mean time I will hold personally and pay all expenses directly on-chain and share the tx history to everyone.
